        "text": "|  |  |  |  |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| **Adamantine Items** | **Hardness** | **HP** | **BT** |\n| **Thin Items** |  |\n| Standard-grade | 10 | 40 | 20 |\n| High-grade | 13 | 52 | 26 |\n| **Items** |  |\n| Standard-grade | 14 | 56 | 28 |\n| High-grade | 17 | 68 | 34 |\n| **Structure** |  |\n| Standard-grade | 28 | 112 | 56 |\n| High-grade | 34 | 136 | 68 |\n\n  \n*Rules for Special Materials*",
        "type": "section"
